unittitle_ssm: Records of the Office of the Assistant to the Chancellor/President (James W. Armsey)
abstract_ssm: This collection is comprised of the papers of James W. Armsey, who worked as the Assistant to the Chancellor, Henry T. Heald, at New York University (NYU) for four years starting in 1952. It is made up of clippings, personal letters, and public relations documents.
